text: Symphytocarpus is a genus of Amoebozoa in the family Stemonitidaceae. , there are nine species in the genus. ==Species== *Symphytocarpus amaurochaetoides *Symphytocarpus confluens *Symphytocarpus cristatus *Symphytocarpus flaccidus *Symphytocarpus fusiformis *Symphytocarpus herbaticus *Symphytocarpus impexus *Symphytocarpus syncarpus *Symphytocarpus trechisporus ==References== Category:Myxogastria Category:Amoebozoa genera
